565
00:49:36,307 --> 00:49:38,099
They wouldn't dare.

566
00:49:42,521 --> 00:49:45,565
They are not so stupid as they look.

567
00:50:37,618 --> 00:50:38,868
(CRASHING)

568
00:50:40,079 --> 00:50:42,080
(CLAMOURING IN ITALIAN)

569
00:50:49,797 --> 00:50:51,256
