646
00:59:35,030 --> 00:59:37,823
and everybody is gonna sit
in the back of the motor.

647
00:59:37,908 --> 00:59:41,285
Charlie, me in the back of the motor,
with my asthma?

648
00:59:47,626 --> 00:59:51,504
