We'll have to get it back.

832
01:36:16,020 --> 01:36:17,855
Get back! Get back!

833
01:36:24,821 --> 01:36:28,365
Now hold still. Don't move.
Don't move at all.

834
01:36:32,954 --> 01:36:37,958
